   "end": "7.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich zitiere:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.640", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gerichte sind der Reparaturbetrieb f\u00fcr die politischen und b\u00fcrokratischen Vers\u00e4umnisse der letzten Jahre."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das schrieb 2017 die \u201eAugsburger Allgemeine\u201c"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr pointiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "grob vereinfachend und auch nicht ganz gerecht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt darin aber zumindest einen Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dem man ins Nachdenken \u00fcber die gewiss nicht europ\u00e4isch-solidarisch bew\u00e4ltigte Massenflucht und \u00fcber unsere sehr komplexen Regelungsversuche derselben Situation kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Ergebnis war dies unweigerlich tats\u00e4chlich eine Arbeitsbeschaffung f\u00fcr viele Anw\u00e4ltinnen und Anw\u00e4lte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.080", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Anw\u00e4ltinnen und Anw\u00e4lte berichten uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass unterschiedliche Spruchk\u00f6rper in demselben Verwaltungsgericht zu ganz unterschiedlichen Ergebnissen kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Gerichte sind in der Tat so etwas wie die Produktionsst\u00e4tten von Urteilen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
